title: My Home Home Cultural Vegetarian Restaurant - temporarily closed
description: Chinese name: 我家家文化主题素食餐厅, address: 朝阳区农展馆北路枣营北里15号宾都苑1楼(京客隆对面). The restaurant is decorated in Chinese traditional cultural theme. No onion, garlic, leek, shallot, chive, spring onion.
